The player's implementation is incomplete and currently failing. Although the player claims `AC-001` is complete, the `test_output_summary` explicitly shows a failure in `test_gives_up` (`AssertionError: expected 3 calls, got 1`), which indicates that the retry logic is not functioning as intended (it is not retrying the specified number of times). Additionally, the player admits that exponential backoff (`AC-002`) has not been implemented, and since the tests failed, the requirement to provide unit tests proving the behavior (`AC-003`) has not been met.

